96
00:05:32,957 --> 00:05:34,349
and surrounded...

97
00:05:34,866 --> 00:05:38,089
a division of Americans
in a little town called Bastogne,

98
00:05:38,973 --> 00:05:42,649
freezing, starving and running out
of ammunition, but they knew...

99
00:05:42,790 --> 00:05:44,730
