100
00:05:44,840 --> 00:05:46,326
Just before Christmas,

101
00:05:46,483 --> 00:05:49,139
the Nazis sent a note

102
00:05:49,239 --> 00:05:50,981
to the American commander

103
00:05:51,081 --> 00:05:53,200
telling him that he could

104
00:05:53,300 --> 00:05:55,320
surrender and save the rt of his men,

105
00:05:55,420 --> 00:05:57,161
or they could stay and fight.

106
00:05:57,411 --> 00:05:59,054
The American commander

107
00:05:59,187 --> 00:06:02,598
