to the Wehrmacht commander,

108
00:06:03,877 --> 00:06:05,801
and it said...
- ... "Nuts."

109
00:06:08,117 --> 00:06:09,344
Why did he say, "Nuts"?

110
00:06:09,444 --> 00:06:11,091
