119
00:06:36,720 --> 00:06:38,394
Have a cup of coffee, Stanley.

120
00:06:39,795 --> 00:06:40,796
Here.

121
00:06:42,142 --> 00:06:43,534
Well, what's this?

122
00:06:44,097 --> 00:06:46,644
As your brother's best man,
you are required to give a toast,

123
00:06:46,744 --> 00:06:48,713
so I wrote down a few thoughts,

124
00:06:48,813 --> 00:06:50,985
some things that
you might want to say.

125
00:06:51,525 --> 00:06:53,355
You think I was going to wing it?

126
00:06:57,099 --> 00:06:59,368
Let's go take some pictures, okay?

127
