131
00:07:22,964 --> 00:07:24,259
The one restriction...

132
00:07:24,377 --> 00:07:27,881
is that no one can know
where you're getting this information.

133
00:07:28,007 --> 00:07:31,527
Tell them I'm... scouting in the field,
tell them what you want...

134
00:07:31,627 --> 00:07:33,783
but the satellite must remain a secret.

135
00:07:37,131 --> 00:07:38,133
Sounds good.

136
00:07:38,832 --> 00:07:40,558
- That's it?
- What do you want me to say?

137
00:07:40,675 --> 00:07:43,082
I get it. Man has a satellite.
Doesn't want anyone to know.

138
00:07:43,182 --> 00:07:45,056
- But...
- I am about to go to war,

139
00:07:45,156 --> 00:07:47,890
with New Bern, Kansas,
the home of the nearest Costco.

140
00:07:48,086 --> 00:07:50,746
